---
title: Herbs De Provence Chicken with a Farro Caprese Salad
description: In our dream life, we’d spend our days frolicking in lavender fields in the south of France. Until then, we have this chicken dish, which features thighs seasoned with herbs de Provence, an herb blend that puts those floral aromatics first. Underneath, you’ve got tender zucchini and a farro, tomato, and mozzarella jumble that’s studded with shreds of fresh basil—call it a grain-filled twist on caprese salad, if you will.
